# Project Structure Guide

This is a Next.js project with tRPC integration. Here's the main structure:

## Core Files
- [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Main page component
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) - Next.js configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts

## Key Directories
- `src/app/` - Contains pages and layouts (Next.js App Router)
- `src/app/_components/` - Reusable React components
- `src/app/api/` - API routes
- `src/trpc/` - tRPC configuration and routers
- `src/server/` - Server-side code and business logic
- `prisma/` - Database schema and migrations

## Configuration Files
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [prettier.config.js](mdc:prettier.config.js) - Code formatting rules
- [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js) - CSS processing configuration
- [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js) - Linting rules
